{"word":"ὑπέρα","slug":"ὑπέρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n107184\" key=\"u(pe/ra\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπέρα</orth> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ῠ]</pron>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὑπέρ</etym>) an <sense id=\"n107184.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">upper rope</tr_>: mostly in pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπέραι,</foreign> the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">braces</tr_> attached to the ends of the sailyards (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐπίκρια</etym>), by means of which the sails are shifted fore and aft, acc. to the direction of the wind, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:260\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.260</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg066:4:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ DMort.\">DMort.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1</biblScope> </bibl>: prov. of those who drop the substance to grasp a shadow, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀφεὶς τὴν ὑ. τὸν πόδα διώκει</foreign> he lets go <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the brace</tr_> to catch at the sheet, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0030.tlg007:181\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hyp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">181</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n107184.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπέραι,</foreign> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὕπερα, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> (s. v.l.).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}